Features:

Pressing P or Escape pauses the game
Pressing R or Space resumes the game

Pressing T restarts game
Holding Left Shift + T resets highscore with game restart

Secrets:

Pressing Q summons Qazi and pauses and after makes Qazi go away and resumes
Chance of Fancy Qazi

Press L for laser
Press 3 cat sounds play
Press E prints Eurler's number

If enabled:
Press C rolls credit picture
Clicking pokes computer